font-size:20px;"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">SOX S4 Control Audit Automation</span></h2></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-k0p06mvp" class="Z_l5lU ku3DBC zQ9jDz qvSjx3 Vq6kJx comp-k0p06mvp wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:17px;"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Technologies: Python, SAP/Fiori, SAP-scripting, Excel, Word-automation, encryption</span></p></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-k0p06mvs" class="Z_l5lU ku3DBC zQ9jDz qvSjx3 Vq6kJx comp-k0p06mvs wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><ul class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:14px;">
<li class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:14px;">Problem Statement: Manual generation of audit workpapers and EY narratives for SAP transactions across 55 controls.</p>
</li>
<li class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:14px;">Solution: Developed an end-to-end Python tool that navigates SAP &amp; Fiori, extracts relevant SAP data and website fields, downloads Excel/Word documents &amp; screenshots, embeds them into workpapers, and securely manages user credentials via two-way encryption.</p>
</li>
<li class="wixui-rich-text__text">

<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:14px;">Value Add: Unified six audit processes within a single platform, enabling live data access, reducing manual effort, and improving data accuracy and reporting efficiency.</p>
</li>
</ul></div><!--/$--></div></div></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9vgah" class="KaEeLN comp-mhh9vgah"><div class="uYj0Sg wixui-box" data-testid="container-bg"></div><div data-mesh-id="comp-mhh9vgahinlineContent" data-testid="inline-content" class=""><div data-mesh-id="comp-mhh9vgahinlineContent-gridContainer" data-testid="mesh-container-content"><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9vgam" class="jbrj02 comp-mhh9vgam"><div class="IvR70V wixui-box" data-testid="container-bg"></div><div data-mesh-id="comp-mhh9vgaminlineContent" data-testid="inline-content" class=""><div data-mesh-id="comp-mhh9vgaminlineContent-gridContainer" data-testid="mesh-container-content"></div></div></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9vgan" class="Z_l5lU ku3DBC zQ9jDz qvSjx3 Vq6kJx comp-mhh9vgan wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><h2 class="font_6 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:20px;"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Database Administration for ORT</span></h2></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9vgao" class="Z_l5lU ku3DBC zQ9jDz qvSjx3 Vq6kJx comp-mhh9vgao wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:14px;"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Full-Stack Developer</span></p></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9vgap" class="Z_l5lU ku3DBC zQ9jDz qvSjx3 Vq6kJx comp-mhh9vgap wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><p class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:1.5em; font-size:17px;"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Technologies: SQL Server, Stored Procedures, Database Migration</span></p></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9vgaq" class="Z_l5lU ku3DBC zQ9jDz qvSjx3 Vq6kJx comp-mhh9vgaq wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><ul class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:14px;">
<li class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:14px;">Problem Statement: A customer experience database required setup, migration, and ongoing performance management to support real-time analytics and reporting.</p>
</li>
<li class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:14px;">Solution: Installed and maintained the SQL Server database for ORT; designed tables, views and stored procedures to manage data extraction and insertion; migrated data from local desktop to server environment; monitored database efficiency, upgraded existing structures, ensured access, uptime and data integrity; planned and coordinated storage and capacity requirements.</p>
</li>
<li class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:14px;">Value Add: Ensured robust, high-performance database infrastructure supporting live audit tooling, enhancing data reliability and operational efficiency.</p>
</li>
</ul></div><!--/$--></div></div></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9vl8o" class="KaEeLN comp-mhh9vl8o"><div class="uYj0Sg wixui-box" data-testid="container-bg"></div><div data-mesh-id="comp-mhh9vl8oinlineContent" data-testid="inline-content" class=""><div data-mesh-id="comp-mhh9vl8oinlineContent-gridContainer" data-testid="mesh-container-content"><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9vl8t" class="jbrj02 comp-mhh9vl8t"><div class="IvR70V wixui-box" data-testid="container-bg"></div><div data-mesh-id="comp-mhh9vl8tinlineContent" data-testid="inline-content" class=""><div data-mesh-id="comp-mhh9vl8tinlineContent-gridContainer" data-testid="mesh-container-content"></div></div></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9vl8t3" class="Z_l5lU ku3DBC zQ9jDz qvSjx3 Vq6kJx comp-mhh9vl8t3 wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><h2 class="font_6 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:20px;"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Attribute Measurement System</span></h2></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9vl8u4" class="Z_l5lU ku3DBC zQ9jDz qvSjx3 Vq6kJx comp-mhh9vl8u4 wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:14px;"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Full-Stack Developer</span></p></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9vl8v4" class="Z_l5lU ku3DBC zQ9jDz qvSjx3 Vq6kJx comp-mhh9vl8v4 wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><p class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:1.5em; font-size:17px;"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Technologies: InfoPath, SharePoint Designer, VBA</span></p></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9vl8w3" class="Z_l5lU ku3DBC zQ9jDz qvSjx3 Vq6kJx comp-mhh9vl8w3 wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><ul class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:14px;">
<li class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:14px;">Problem Statement: Correlation analysis was needed to compare case-categorisation decisions between team members and SMEs.</p>
</li>
<li class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:14px;">Solution: Developed a full-stack assessment tool using InfoPath forms for user input, SharePoint Designer workflows and VBA scripting to compute performance comparisons (team member vs SME vs team), validate data, and visualise results.</p>
</li>
<li class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:14px;">Value Add: Delivered an automated assessment and reporting workflow, enabling transparent performance comparisons and improving efficiency in categorisation processes.</p>
</li>
</ul></div><!--/$--></div></div></div><!--/$--></div></div></div><!--/$--></div></section><!--/$--></div></div></section><!--/$--></div></div></div><!--/$--></div></div></div></div></main><footer id="SITE_FOOTER" class="AT7o0U SITE_FOOTER wixui-footer" tabindex="-1"><div class="lvxhkV"></div><div class="cKxVkc"><div class="vlM3HR"></div><div class="VrZrC0"><div data-mesh-id="SITE_FOOTERinlineContent" data-testid="inline-content" class=""><div data-mesh-id="SITE_FOOTERinlineContent-gridContainer" data-testid="mesh-container-content"><!--$--><section id="comp-k0kphh2d" class="comp-k0kphh2d CohWsy wixui-column-strip"><div id="bgLayers_comp-k0kphh2d" data-hook="bgLayers" data-motion-part="BG_LAYER comp-k0kphh2d" class="if7Vw2"><div data-testid="colorUnderlay" class="tcElKx i1tH8h"></div><div id="bgMedia_comp-k0kphh2d" data-motion-part="BG_MEDIA comp-k0kphh2d" class="wG8dni"></div></div><div data-testid="columns" class="V5AUxf"><!--$--><div id="comp-k0kphh32" class="comp-k0kphh32 YzqVVZ wixui-column-strip__column"><div id="bgLayers_comp-k0kphh32" data-hook="bgLayers" data-motion-part="BG_LAYER comp-k0kphh32" class="MW5IWV"><div data-testid="colorUnderlay" class="LWbAav Kv1aVt"></div><div id="bgMedia_comp-k0kphh32" data-motion-part="BG_MEDIA comp-k0kphh32" class="VgO9Yg"></div></div><div data-mesh-id="comp-k0kphh32inlineContent" data-testid="inline-content" class=""><div data-mesh-id="comp-k0kphh32inlineContent-gridContainer" data-testid="mesh-container-content"><!--$--><div id="comp-k2398tck" class="Z_l5lU ku3DBC zQ9jDz qvSjx3 Vq6kJx comp-k2398tck wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><p class="font_9 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:14px;"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">© 2035 by Jayanthan Rajendran.<br class="wixui-rich-text__text">
